  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of AR08 for the Treatment of Vasomotor Symptoms (VMS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Forced Titration, Dose-ranging Study of AR08 in the Treatment of Vasomotor Symptoms (VMS) in Menopausal Females: A Proof-of-Concept Study</official_title>
